    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is an exceptional 981-generation Cayman S, featuring the venerable 3.4L naturally aspirated flat-six engine with Direct Fuel Injection (DFI) and VarioCam Plus. This specimen is paired with a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle, offering unparalleled driver engagement. The chassis is equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and Porsche Torque Vectoring (PTV) with a mechanical rear differential lock, ensuring surgical precision through the apex. This vehicle has been maintained to an exacting standard; the DME report confirms zero ignitions in higher RPM ranges, and the cooling system remains pressurized to factory spec. With no bolster wear on the sport seats and a concours-level undercarriage, this is a turn-key example for the discerning collector who demands mechanical integrity and linear power delivery up to the 7,400 RPM redline.",
      "price": 48500.0,
